        <section class="faq-section">
            <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2>What services do you offer?</h2>
                <p>We provide professional home services including electrical repairs, plumbing, carpentry, and more. You can check our full range of services on the Services page.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2>How do I book a service?</h2>
                <p>You can easily book a service by contacting us through the website or by calling our customer support. Simply select your required service, and we'll schedule a time that's convenient for you.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2>What areas do you serve?</h2>
                <p>We offer our services in multiple areas. You can check if we operate in your area by visiting our "Service Areas" page or by contacting us directly.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2>How much do your services cost?</h2>
                <p>The cost of services varies depending on the type of work required. For a more accurate estimate, please contact us with the details of your requirements, and we’ll provide a quote.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2>Are the professionals licensed?</h2>
                <p>Yes, all of our professionals are highly skilled and licensed to provide the services we offer. We ensure that our team members have the necessary certifications and experience.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2>Do you offer emergency services?</h2>
                <p>Yes, we offer emergency services for electrical, plumbing, and carpentry issues. If you require urgent assistance, please contact us directly to arrange immediate service.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2>How can I contact customer support?</h2>
                <p>You can contact our customer support via email, phone, or the contact form on our website. Visit the Contact Us page for more details.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h2>Do you offer warranties on your work?</h2>
                <p>Yes, we provide warranties on our work to ensure customer satisfaction. If any issues arise within the warranty period, please get in touch with us, and we’ll resolve the issue promptly.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
